<a href="http://allafrica.com/stories/201302210556.html" target="_self">http://allafrica.com/stories/201302210556.html</a></p><p><i>The Namibian</i>, ‘Nam to talk to EU about beef import rule’, 28 February 2013</p><p>
<a href="http://allafrica.com/stories/201302280773.html" target="_self">http://allafrica.com/stories/201302280773.html</a></p><p><i>New Era</i>, ‘New EU residency rule will hurt producers’, 14 February 2013</p><p>
